\pard\plain \sl288\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b0\i0\cf1  That was a question, and in his model of reality  Every word was  ignorance. This was his \loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8216\'91why\u8217\'92.  voice took the length of that measure and tried to map it onto omniscience. He\u8217\'92d built a structure out of words, and there were stray ends. Why? That \u8216\'91why\u8217\'92 was his. He demanded answers from himself. }}